title: The Ramones Loco live Sire Records Relaunch 1992
description:
This is the version of locolive barcelona concert recorded on 11 and 12 March. 1992 version is different, both in their home and in the order of songs, among which four tracks "I Just Wanna Have Something to Do", "Havana Affair" "I Do not Wanna Go Down to be replaced the Basement, "and the hidden track" Carbona Not Glue ".
